Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). In a medium bowl, combine the crabmeat, bell pepper, pimento, mayonnaise, egg, Worcestershire sauce, salt, mustard powder and red pepper sauce. Mix well and spoon into a shallow 1 1/2-quart baking dish. Bake at 350 degrees F (175 degrees C) for 20 to 25 minutes.